                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6536" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0630</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8262 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">授人以“鱼”，不如授人以“渔”：泓森包容性创新发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Teaching people to &quot;fish&quot; is better than giving people &quot;fish&quot;: Hongsen&#39;s development path of inclusive innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李海红，张霜，周旭，何蓉，雍梦婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广元市泓森农业科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">泓森；BOP群体；包容性创新；精准扶贫；竞争优势；2022百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hongsen; BOP group; Inclusive innovation; Targeted poverty reduction; Competitive advantages.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当前中国经济发展进入新常态，但发展不平衡不协调问题依旧突出，金字塔状的贫富不均状况仍然十分明显。精准扶贫虽有效地实现了贫困地区和人民“脱帽”，但如何巩固脱贫攻坚成果，防止返贫，推进全面脱贫和乡村振兴的有效衔接仍需各方关注。尤其西部偏远山区，交通不便等因素，造成这些地区“脱贫攻坚战”难攻难守。因而，与农民有天然联系的农业企业应如何迎接挑战，创造机遇，成为亟待思考的问题。本案例以广元市泓森农业科技有限公司 （简称：泓森）为背景，结合丁彬瀚自身经历和泓森的坎坷发展历程，描写了泓森基于BOP群体 ，进行包容性创新的实践。展示了泓森在逐步突破自我并不断发展壮大的过程中，是如何参与“精准扶贫”，履行社会责任并打造其独特竞争优势的。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At present, China&#39;s economic development has entered the new normal, but the problem of unbalanced and uncoordinated development is still prominent, and the pyramid shaped inequality between the rich and the poor is still obvious. Although targeted poverty reduction has effectively achieved the &quot;off-the-hat&quot; of the poverty-stricken areas and people, how to consolidate the results of poverty alleviation, prevent poverty, and promote the effective connection of comprehensive poverty alleviation and rural revitalization still needs attention. Especially in the remote mountainous areas of western China, inconvenient transportation and other factors have made the &quot;poverty alleviation battle&quot; difficult to defend in these areas. Therefore, how to meet the challenges and create opportunities for agricultural enterprises that have natural connections with farmers has become a problem that needs to be considered urgently. This case is based on the background of Guangyuan Hongsen Agricultural Technology Co., Ltd. (abbreviated as: Hongsen), combined with Ding Binhan&#39;s own experience and the bumpy development history of Hongsen, describing Hongsen&#39;s practice of inclusive innovation based on the BOP group. It shows how Hongsen has participated in the &quot; targeted poverty reduction&quot; to fulfill its social responsibilities and build its unique competitive advantages in the process of gradual breakthroughs and continuous development and growth.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">包容性创新中的BOP群体；包容性创新驱动因素；包容性创新的路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
